comments: Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Gobert (UTA) sets the pick in Dozier's (DEN) path and absorbs the contact when contact occurs.

Replay review of the foul called on Ingles (UTA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Ingles (UTA) drives through Dozier's (DEN) body, who is established in a legal position in Ingles' path.
Murray (DEN) and Ingles (UTA) engage and separate off-ball.
Ingles (UTA) briefly brings his arm across Jokic's (DEN) body after the screen and slides it off in a continuous motion.
Mitchell (UTA) initiates some contact with Murray (DEN) during the rebound, but he does not prevent Murray from gathering the ball.
Murray (DEN) and Bogdanovic (UTA) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.

Though Conley (UTA) initially makes contact with the ball, he does not dislodge it. Conley then makes more than marginal contact with Murray's (DEN) arm during his shooting motion on the play at the basket.
Morris (DEN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Mitchell (UTA) in transition.
Jokic (DEN) sets the pick in Bogdanovic's (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Mitchell (UTA) initiates some contact with Craig (DEN) during the rebound, but he does not prevent Craig from gathering the ball.
Mitchell (UTA) briefly grasps Craig (DEN) before releasing during the loose ball situation.
Gobert (UTA) makes incidental contact with Jokic's (DEN) body after the release on his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) and Gobert (UTA) briefly engage and separate in the backcourt.
Jokic (DEN) initiates marginal contact with Gobert (UTA) in the backcourt and doesn't affect his FOM.
Bogdanovic (UTA) is firming up in a picking position in Harris's (DEN) path when contact occurs, and he absorbs the contact.
Conley (UTA) collapses his forearm when contact occurs with Murray (DEN), and Conley does not extend his arm at the end of the drive.
Conley (UTA) commits a take foul on Harris (DEN).
Gobert (UTA) initiates some contact with Harris (DEN) in transition, but he does not prevent Harris from maintaining his defensive path.
Jokic (DEN) makes incidental high-five contact with Bogdanovic's (UTA) hand after the release on his jump shot attempt.
